data.eml:eml: Three new Macropsini (Hemiptera: Cicadellidae) leafhopper species from Australia

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Yang, Liyuan, Dietrich, Christopher H., Zhang, Yalin (2017): Three new Macropsini (Hemiptera: Cicadellidae) leafhopper species from Australia. Zootaxa 4273 (2): 271-278, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4273.2.7
